    <item>
      <title>亚德尼称美联储今年已不再降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/yardeni-says-the-fed-is-done-cutting-rates-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Yardeni Research 总裁 Ed Yardeni 表示，美联储今年的降息行动已经结束，他预计第三季度的收益将创下历史新高。他正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/yardeni-says-the-fed-is-done-cutting-rates-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:12:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富国银行警告亚马逊云计算业务“实力不足” 股价遭下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-cut-as-wells-fargo-warns-cloud-strength-not-enough</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司 (Amazon.com Inc.) 股价周一在盘前交易中下跌，此前分析师罕见下调了其评级，理由是担心明年的利润率趋势，而云计算业务的增长不太可能弥补这一影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-cut-as-wells-fargo-warns-cloud-strength-not-enough</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>橄榄油危机缓解，顶级生产国产量激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/olive-oil-crunch-eases-as-spain-forecasts-crop-to-jump-by-48</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本季西班牙橄榄油产量预计将增长近一半，缓解因两次歉收而推高价格的供应紧张局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/olive-oil-crunch-eases-as-spain-forecasts-crop-to-jump-by-48</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Crossmark 的 Bob Doll 表示，美国将面临“坎坷的着陆”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/us-in-for-a-bumpy-landing-says-crossmark-s-bob-doll-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Crossmark Global Investments 首席执行官兼首席投资官 Bob Doll 表示，9 月份就业报告发布后，“通胀问题再次被摆上台面”，并解释了为什么他认为美国经济“明显放缓”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/us-in-for-a-bumpy-landing-says-crossmark-s-bob-doll-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:10:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰亿万富翁家庭纠纷导致养老金基金股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/billionaire-solorz-ousts-sons-from-polish-utility-s-board</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰亿万富翁齐格蒙特·索洛兹 (Zygmunt Solorz) 将他的两个儿子从他的公用事业公司赶了出去，加深了家族对企业集团控制权的争夺，导致估值下降，并引发了主要少数投资者的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/billionaire-solorz-ousts-sons-from-polish-utility-s-board</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马尔代夫重新转向印度以缓解中国债务压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/maldives-seeks-to-repair-ties-with-india-as-debt-crisis-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尔代夫总统一年前上台，力图将印度排除在该国事务之外，与中国拉近关系。如今，随着债务危机的临近以及中国先前发放的贷款即将到期，他正在新德里寻求修复两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/maldives-seeks-to-repair-ties-with-india-as-debt-crisis-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 05:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员减少对美联储降息的押注，股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员削减对美联储降息的押注，导致股市下跌，美国 10 年期国债收益率超过 4%。市场在等待以色列是否会对上周的导弹袭击进行报复，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:37:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周全球大宗商品值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中东冲突升级、乌克兰战争、恶劣天气和供应链瓶颈导致大宗商品价格飙升。黄金价格上涨使得用黄金购买布伦特原油更加便宜。巴西玉米作物面临的风险也推高了谷物价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
